        <item>
          <title>Pacers run over Jazz in fourth quarter in 140-112 win</title>
          <description><![CDATA[INDIANAPOLIS (ABC4 Sports) - The Utah Jazz hung with the Indiana Pacers for three quarters, trailing by just four points going into the fourth. But Indiana outscored Utah in the final quarter, 42-18 en route to a 140-112 win. The Jazz have lost eight in a row and 18 of its last 19 games.]]></description>
